get.description: Get a list of device objects.

parameters.name: airflow
parameters.description:
* `front-to-rear` - Front to rear
* `rear-to-front` - Rear to front
* `left-to-right` - Left to right
* `right-to-left` - Right to left
* `side-to-rear` - Side to rear
* `rear-to-side` - Rear to side
* `bottom-to-top` - Bottom to top
* `top-to-bottom` - Top to bottom
* `passive` - Passive
* `mixed` - Mixed

parameters.name: limit
parameters.description: Number of results to return per page.

parameters.name: offset
parameters.description: The initial index from which to return the results.

parameters.name: ordering
parameters.description: Which field to use when ordering the results.

post.description: Post a list of device objects.

put.description: Put a list of device objects.

patch.description: Patch a list of device objects.

delete.description: Delete a list of device objects.
